sql: SELECT r.order_details FROM Orders AS r WHERE  r.customer_id > 17 ORDER BY r.order_details ASC

SELECT other_shipment_details, shipment_tracking_number FROM Invoices JOIN Shipments JOIN Orders ON Orders.order_id = Shipments.order_id AND Shipments.invoice_number = Invoices.invoice_number WHERE  Shipments.invoice_number >= 90 OR shipment_date = (SELECT AVG(shipment_date) FROM Shipments WHERE  order_id > 29) GROUP BY shipment_tracking_number LIMIT 4
SELECT order_id FROM Orders WHERE customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  customer_id = 12 LIMIT 5
SELECT shipment_tracking_number, other_shipment_details, invoice_number FROM Shipments WHERE  order_id > 61 GROUP BY invoice_number HAVING AVG(order_id) > 3 ORDER BY invoice_number ASC

SELECT shipment_tracking_number, order_details FROM Invoices JOIN Shipments JOIN Orders ON Orders.order_id = Shipments.order_id AND Shipments.invoice_number = Invoices.invoice_number WHERE customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  Invoices.invoice_number <= 100

SELECT customer_id, customer_id, customer_details FROM Customers WHERE customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Orders WHERE  customer_id > 85 AND Customers.customer_id = customer_id) GROUP BY customer_details LIMIT 2
SELECT MAX(Customers.customer_id), customer_name FROM Customers JOIN Orders ON Orders.customer_id = Customers.customer_id WHERE  order_id < 7 ORDER BY customer_name ASC
SELECT AVG(b.customer_id), b.order_status FROM Orders AS b WHERE  b.order_id > 48 GROUP BY b.order_status
SELECT other_shipment_details FROM Shipments WHERE  shipment_id != 39 LIMIT 2
SELECT order_item_status, order_item_details, product_id FROM Order_Items WHERE product_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  order_item_id != 71 GROUP BY product_id ORDER BY order_item_details ASC
SELECT invoice_details, invoice_date FROM Invoices WHERE  invoice_number != 30 GROUP BY invoice_date

SELECT COUNT(Shipment_Items.shipment_id), COUNT(DISTINCT Shipments.shipment_id), COUNT(DISTINCT Shipment_Items.order_item_id) FROM Shipment_Items JOIN Order_Items JOIN Shipments JOIN Orders ON Orders.order_id = Shipments.order_id AND Order_Items.order_item_id = Shipment_Items.order_item_id AND Shipment_Items.shipment_id = Shipments.shipment_id WHERE Order_Items.order_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR order_item_id IN (SELECT order_item_id FROM Order_Items)
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT invoice_date), invoice_number FROM Invoices WHERE  invoice_number <= 70
SELECT MAX(o.customer_id), o.customer_details FROM Customers AS o WHERE  o.customer_id > 59 ORDER BY o.customer_details ASC
SELECT customer_id, customer_name FROM Customers WHERE  customer_id != 51
SELECT SUM(h.shipment_id), h.shipment_id FROM Shipments AS h WHERE  h.invoice_number != 14 ORDER BY h.shipment_id ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT shipment_date), Shipment_Items.shipment_id FROM Shipments JOIN Shipment_Items ON Shipment_Items.shipment_id = Shipments.shipment_id WHERE  order_item_id < 43
SELECT MAX(product_id), COUNT(order_id), MIN(order_id) FROM Order_Items

SELECT order_item_status FROM Products JOIN Order_Items ON Order_Items.product_id = Products.product_id WHERE Order_Items.product_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR product_name = (SELECT MAX(product_name) FROM Products WHERE  product_id != 40 LIMIT 7) ORDER BY order_item_status ASC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Orders.order_id), shipment_tracking_number FROM Customers JOIN Shipments JOIN Orders ON Orders.customer_id = Customers.customer_id AND Orders.order_id = Shipments.order_id WHERE Shipments.order_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Shipments WHERE  invoice_number > 65 AND Orders.order_id = order_id)
SELECT shipment_id FROM Shipments JOIN Orders ON Orders.order_id = Shipments.order_id WHERE shipment_id < (SELECT MAX(shipment_id) FROM Shipment_Items AS r)
SELECT MIN(invoice_number) FROM Invoices WHERE  invoice_number = 23 LIMIT 2
SELECT shipment_id, order_id, shipment_tracking_number FROM Shipments WHERE  order_id > 53 GROUP BY shipment_tracking_number HAVING MAX(invoice_number) = 9 ORDER BY order_id DESC
SELECT COUNT(product_id) FROM Products WHERE product_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Order_Items WHERE  order_id = 39 AND Products.product_id = product_id)
SELECT MIN(order_id), order_status FROM Orders WHERE  customer_id <= 19
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT product_name), COUNT(DISTINCT product_details), product_name FROM Products WHERE  product_id <= 79 GROUP BY product_name ORDER BY product_name ASC

SELECT order_item_id, other_shipment_details FROM Shipments JOIN Shipment_Items ON Shipment_Items.shipment_id = Shipments.shipment_id WHERE  order_id > 4 OR invoice_number IN (SELECT invoice_number FROM Shipments WHERE  order_id > 53) ORDER BY other_shipment_details ASC

SELECT MIN(x.customer_id), x.customer_id, Customers.customer_name FROM Customers AS x JOIN Customers ON Customers.customer_id = x.customer_id WHERE customer_id <= (SELECT MAX(customer_id) FROM Customers WHERE  customer_id <= 27)

SELECT invoice_details FROM Shipments JOIN Invoices JOIN Shipment_Items JOIN Order_Items ON Order_Items.order_item_id = Shipment_Items.order_item_id AND Shipments.invoice_number = Invoices.invoice_number AND Shipment_Items.shipment_id = Shipments.shipment_id WHERE  Shipment_Items.shipment_id < 18
SELECT AVG(l.order_id), l.order_item_details FROM Order_Items AS l ORDER BY l.order_item_details ASC LIMIT 3
SELECT SUM(customer_id), MAX(customer_id) FROM Customers WHERE  customer_id <= 39 LIMIT 10
SELECT product_id, order_item_status FROM Order_Items WHERE  order_item_id < 88 GROUP BY order_item_status HAVING MAX(product_id) >= 10 ORDER BY product_id ASC
SELECT Orders.order_id FROM Shipments JOIN Orders ON Orders.order_id = Shipments.order_id WHERE  Orders.order_id != 93 LIMIT 4
SELECT AVG(invoice_number), invoice_number, invoice_details FROM Invoices WHERE  invoice_number < 81 GROUP BY invoice_details HAVING MIN(invoice_number) >= 81
SELECT customer_id, customer_id, customer_details FROM Customers WHERE  customer_id > 54 GROUP BY customer_details
